                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>of this subject by <sic>ze</sic> learned Jewish\n                                        commen-<lb/>-tators. I appeal to you, Rev Sir, as one\n                                        thorough<lb/>-ly acquainted with Jewish literature &amp;\n                                        whom<lb/> studies &amp; researches have qualified him,\n                                        not<lb/> more for <sic>ze</sic> profound philosopher than\n                                                  <sic>ze</sic><lb/> erudite\n                                        metaply<add>?</add>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I enclose this to you<lb/> under cover of my\n                                        friend <persName>Dessan's</persName> epistle, who<lb/> will\n                                        bespeak for mine a favorable reception.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I am, dear Sir,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">your very obt svt</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">C. T. Quintard M.D.</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n                              </p>"
